snippet.title: The Bunny Graveyard - DEMO Trailer
snippet.description:
🐰WISHLIST ON STEAM 🐰
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1892420/The_Bunny_Graveyard/

🐦FOLLOW PICHON GAMES 🐦

Skye and her Handy Pals are looking for a new pal to help them out on her lovely lil' garden! Think you're up for the job?

This trailer contains footage from Chapter 1 of The Bunny Graveyard.

CREDITS:
Gardener Skye voiced by: Courtney Chu
Animated by: Kenneth Alvarez
